        <link href="https://www.yashkarthik.xyz/archive/nft-law"/>
        <updated>2022-02-10T18:30:00.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[NFTs and copyright, both do the same thing - establish a connection between the asset and the creator, providing them with ownership over their work, and enabling uniqueness. The only difference being that NFTs are not (yet) recognized by law.]]></content>
